-- BBVA says expects profit boost from Catalunya Banc purchase
-- 
-- Tue Jul 22, 2014 04:05AM EDT
-- None



MADRID, July 22 (Reuters) - Spain's BBVA <BBVA.MC> said on Tuesday its acquisition of local peer Catalunya Banc would add an average 300 million euros ($405.15 million) annually to its net profit from 2018, and entail 450 million euros in restructuring costs.

